24:59.367 --> 25:01.198
My daughter is missing. 

25:03.687 --> 25:06.997
Please tell me where she is. 

25:18.487 --> 25:20.523
She is not your daughter. 

25:31.407 --> 25:35.320
The father, please come. 

25:59.167 --> 26:04.241
I see swirling red flowers. 

26:04.367 --> 26:11.284
And flowing curtains in the wind, 
as in the footsteps of Satan. 

26:12.887 --> 26:18.280
They come in the night, 
with fire in their eyes. 

26:18.407 --> 26:22.844
Who? Who has come? 
- ... darkness in their heart. 

26:22.967 --> 26:29.520
Her little head is under the bed hiding. 

26:29.647 --> 26:35.324
The cross falls to the floor, as do the curtains. 

26:35.447 --> 26:42.637
The curtains are torn as the man falls. 

26:48.767 --> 26:55.115
The true meaning of enlightenment 
is to see in the dark ... 

26:55.247 --> 26:57.602
with open eyes. 

31:05.407 --> 31:09.116
