31:13.767 --> 31:15.837
Come closer. 

31:17.047 --> 31:21.916
Please, tell me where Toby is. 

31:24.327 --> 31:25.999
Can you see her? 

31:29.887 --> 31:36.998
Do you know the story of the cranes 
from the lost city of the Aztecs? 

31:40.847 --> 31:45.557
On dark, moonless nights ... 

31:45.687 --> 31:50.283
at times, they flew
back to their homeland ... 

31:53.167 --> 31:55.044
to welcome death. 

31:57.367 --> 32:02.202
The darkness that you are trying 
to avoid ... 

32:03.367 --> 32:06.677
says you must return ... 

32:08.487 --> 32:12.002
to your roots. 

32:14.927 --> 32:20.763
Go back.  Return.

33:25.047 --> 33:26.765
Hello. Wait, I can't hear you. 

33:28.567 --> 33:35.837
Josefina? She is working with a client, 
baby. But I am here. 

33:37.607 --> 33:43.204
Should I send her a message?
Who is this anyway? 

33:45.447 --> 33:50.441
Robert? 
Is that you, Robert? 

37:03.727 --> 37:10.519
Do you not hear the phone? 
- Don't you!? We're watching TV. 

37:26.527 --> 37:29.200
Josefina, telephone! Josefina!

37:39.927 --> 37:42.760
Hello? Yes, Josefina. 

37:44.567 --> 37:48.606
My God, Robert. 

37:49.447 --> 37:54.077
It's been so long.
How are you? 

37:54.207 --> 37:58.678
Lorena has become eight or nine? 
- Eleven. 

37:58.807 --> 38:04.404
Eleven! How is she? 
- She was kidnapped two days ago. 

38:04.527 --> 38:12.115
Kidnapped? Blessed Death, 
glorious Death, mighty Death ... 

38:12.247 --> 38:18.925
conquer him who is conquering me, 
like Jesus conquered on the cross, Amen.

38:21.727 --> 38:28.075
Listen, I need your help. 
- Tell me what I can do. 

38:28.207 --> 38:32.644
I must know who brings the girls from
the US these days. 

38:32.767 --> 38:37.841
You think she's taken? 
- I don't know. Hopefully not. 

38:37.967 --> 38:43.678
You know how it goes. Everyone is
quiet but I will ask around a bit. 

38:43.807 --> 38:46.401
Thanks, Josefina. 
- Stay well. 

