Get out of here. 

01:00:18.327 --> 01:00:20.318
Pervert. 

01:00:26.007 --> 01:00:27.804
Until tomorrow. 

01:01:43.027 --> 01:01:45.481
Where is that foreigner, Marco? 

01:03:19.907 --> 01:03:22.020
Ten dollars per hour. 

01:03:24.947 --> 01:03:26.366
Twenty. 

01:10:43.167 --> 01:10:47.001
St Death, this is Robert. 

01:10:48.447 --> 01:10:52.360
I'm back and I'm now faced with you again... 

01:10:55.727 --> 01:10:57.399
for the last time. 

01:11:01.927 --> 01:11:05.840
Dear Death, 
I do not need your protection... 

01:11:07.567 --> 01:11:09.876
but my family does. 

01:11:12.487 --> 01:11:16.082
Protect my loved ones 
against my enemies. 

01:11:40.887 --> 01:11:45.597
conquer him who is conquering me, 
like Jesus conquered on the cross.

