holy of holy, cup to cup. 

01:15:52.647 --> 01:15:56.003
St Death is one of us ... 

01:15:56.127 --> 01:16:03.397
Now our newest daughter,
a wife she is to become. 

01:16:05.607 --> 01:16:08.485
St Death, show us the way. 

01:16:10.047 --> 01:16:12.959
St Death, protect us ... 

01:16:15.807 --> 01:16:22.280
and share this holy communion with us. 

01:16:25.807 --> 01:16:29.004
